Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.62,0:24:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岛田
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.40,0:24:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.55,0:24:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除去成本经费
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.93,0:24:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以买到桌子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.95,0:24:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.22,0:25:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么惊人的销售量
